<h2>HVAC Services We Brand</h2><ul class="services"><li><em>Furnace Installation & Repair</em></li><li><em>Air Conditioning & Ductless Mini-Splits</em></li><li><em>Indoor Air Quality & Duct Cleaning</em></li><li><strong>Commercial HVAC & Rooftop Units</strong></li><li><strong>Geothermal Heating & Cooling</strong></li><li><strong>Boiler & Radiant Heat</strong></li><li><strong>Water Heater Installation</strong></li><li><strong>24/7 Emergency HVAC Service</strong></li></ul><h2>HVAC Van Wrap Design Best Practices</h2><p class="body-text">The most effective HVAC van wraps follow a clear hierarchy: <strong>company name</strong> visible from 100+ feet, <strong>phone number</strong> readable from 50 feet, and <strong>services listed</strong> for close-range reading. We design wraps that work from every angle — crucial because HVAC vans are often viewed from the side while parked in driveways.</p><p class="body-text">We recommend including your <strong>Google review rating</strong>, key service areas, and a clear call to action. Emergency HVAC companies should prominently feature "24/7" messaging and their phone number in the largest possible font. <a href="/fleet-wraps-chicago/" style="color:var(--gold)">Learn about our fleet branding process →</a></p><h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2><div class="faq-item"><h3>How much do HVAC van wraps cost in Chicago?</h3><p>Cargo van wraps start at $2,800–$4,500 for a full wrap. Sprinter vans run $3,500–$5,200. Partial wraps and lettering start at $800–$1,500. Fleet discounts of 5–15% apply for 3+ vehicles.</p></div><div class="faq-item"><h3>What van types do you wrap for HVAC companies?</h3><p>We wrap all HVAC service vans: Ford Transit, Ram ProMaster, Chevy Express, Mercedes Sprinter, NV200, and Transit Connect. We also wrap pickup trucks and box trucks used for HVAC installations.</p></div><div class="faq-item"><h3>How long does an HVAC van wrap last in Chicago weather?</h3><p>Our HVAC van wraps use premium cast vinyl rated for 5–7 years of outdoor durability in Chicago's freeze-thaw climate. Includes a 2-year installation warranty covering lifting, peeling, and bubbling.</p></div><div class="faq-item"><h3>Can you match our existing HVAC brand colors?</h3><p>Absolutely. We do precise Pantone and custom color matching to ensure your van wraps match your existing branding, business cards, uniforms, and website.</p></div><div class="cta-bar"><a href="/estimate/" class="btn btn-primary">Get Your HVAC Van Wrap Quote →</a><a href="tel:+13125971286" class="btn" style="border-color:var(--gold);color:var(--gold)">📞 (312) 597-1286</a></div></div>